754
00:48:18.770 --> 00:48:20.647
The man obsessed.

755
00:48:21.189 --> 00:48:22.774
The drive powerful.

756
00:48:24.192 --> 00:48:26.320
The heart a-pounding!

757
00:48:27.529 --> 00:48:30.490
He is oblivious to the future.

758
00:48:32.075 --> 00:48:34.536
[Martyn] It must have been
