and there was smoke in front of me.

760
00:48:38.248 --> 00:48:40.167
and he was straddled across me.

761
00:48:41.168 --> 00:48:43.378
And just pushing him backwards.

762
00:48:44.004 --> 00:48:46.006
I said.
