823
00:52:40.073 --> 00:52:42.951
I was thinking.
"Why do you keep asking me these things

824
00:52:43.034 --> 00:52:45.871
about dental records.
and teeth. and jaws?"

825
00:52:45.954 --> 00:52:47.080
Then it clicked.

826
00:52:47.914 --> 00:52:49.916
