828
00:52:54.963 --> 00:52:57.132
I remember he bought me
the Fat Larry's Band.

829
00:52:57.215 --> 00:52:58.300
It was called "Zoom."

830
00:52:58.800 --> 00:53:01.761
And every time that record comes on.
