and we loved our mother.

837
00:53:22.490 --> 00:53:23.867
But most memories aren't fun.

838
00:53:24.868 --> 00:53:26.745
Mostly. it was over drugs.

839
00:53:26.828 --> 00:53:29.164
♪ Zoom. you chased… ♪

